com.caverock.androidsvg

Enum SVG.AspectRatioAlignment

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SVG.AspectRatioAlignment>
      • com.caverock.androidsvg.SVG.AspectRatioAlignment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<SVG.AspectRatioAlignment>
    Enclosing class:
    SVG

    public static enum SVG.AspectRatioAlignment
extends java.lang.Enum<SVG.AspectRatioAlignment>
    Determines how the document is to me positioned relative to the viewport (normally the canvas). <0> For the value none, the document is stretched to fit the viewport dimensions. For all other values, the aspect ratio of the document is kept the same but the document is scaled to fit the viewport.
